{"atom_id":"md_AE_assumptions_a011","file":"domains/AE/assumptions.md","line_start":8,"line_end":8,"parent_section":"2. **AE description and coding**","atom_type":"LIST_ITEM","verbatim":"   c. AEDECOD is the preferred term derived by the sponsor from the coding dictionary. It is a required variable and must have a value. It is expected that the reported term (AETERM) will be coded using a standard dictionary such as MedDRA. The sponsor is expected to provide the dictionary name and version used to map the terms utilizing the external codelist element in the Define-XML document.","heading_level":0,"sibling_index":2,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:writer","prompt_version":"P0_writer_md_v1.1+","ts":"2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
